             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am wife of the last witness. (Deposed to the same effect.) He came as a religious man; and I could not have the least suspicion of his having any thing of that sort, he talked so much of honesty, and about prayer and singing, and all that; and I thought he must be upon religious terms; and I could not think a religious person could be a thief: the gentleman he came from, Mr. 
               <persName id="t17900113-99-person935">
                  Luke
                   Holden
               <interp inst="t17900113-99-person935" type="surname" value="Holden"></interp>
