            , was a preacher of the gospel.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>The prosecutor entrusted me with the umbrellas to sell for him: I have a wife and three children, and she lays in of another.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17900113-99-verdict521" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17900113-99-verdict521" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>He was detained for obtaining two umbrellas by false pretences.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
